OL,3,CPlymouth City Council's #15million
OL,4,Cplan to ease the housing crisis
OL,6,FPlymouth City council has vowed to
OL,7,Ftake urgent action to tackle the
OL,8,Fgrowing housing crisis.
OL,10,FThe council has agreed its budget for
OL,11,Fthe coming year, which will include
OL,12,F#15million set aside to buy up
OL,13,Fproperties as an alternative to B&Bs
OL,14,Fand hotels for people at risk of
OL,15,Fhomelessness.
OL,17,FRecord numbers of people are now in
OL,18,Ftemporary accommodation and the
OL,19,Fdirector of a leading housing charity
OL,20,Fhas told ITV News the city needs a
OL,21,Fradical solution.
