OL,6,FMike Taylor, who runs PATH (Plymouth
OL,7,FAccess to Housing) said: "We are in a
OL,8,Freally difficult time in terms of
OL,9,Fpeople just getting access to housing.
OL,11,F"We're seeing more and more working
OL,12,Fpeople, single people, families
OL,13,Fpresenting as homeless because they
OL,14,Fcan't afford what a couple of years
OL,15,Fago people could afford. It feels like
OL,16,Fthe rug is being pulled from under
OL,17,Fpeople.
