OL,6,F"Local authorities are working with
OL,7,Fwith us, charities, service providers
OL,8,Fand really trying to look at answers
OL,9,Fin terms of temporary accommodation
OL,10,Fand longer term accommodation,
OL,11,Fincluding looking to buy more
OL,12,Fproperty."
OL,14,FCouncil leader Tudor Evans said:
OL,15,F"Times are indeed tough for everyone.
OL,16,FBut we need to focus on what is
OL,17,Fimportant.
