OL,6,F"Our budget for next year aims to
OL,7,Fprotect frontline, visible services
OL,8,Fthat Plymouth residents value, such as
OL,9,Fmore grass cutting in residential
OL,10,Fareas, tackling potholes, street
OL,11,Fcleaning and it allocates the funding
OL,12,Fneeded to meet the rising demand for
OL,13,Four social care and homelessness
OL,14,Fservices that protect the most
OL,15,Fvulnerable in our community."
